getall\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/alarms/getAll\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">alarms.getAll() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>获取所有的 alarm.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"alarms.clear\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/alarms/clear\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">alarms.clear() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>清除指定名称的 alarm.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"alarms.clearall\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/alarms/clearAll\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">alarms.clearAll() (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>清除所有的 alarm.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"事件","title":"事件","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"alarms.onalarm\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/alarms/onAlarm\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">alarms.onAlarm (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>当 alarm 发生的时候触发。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"webextensions.api.alarms","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/alarms/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> The \"Chrome incompatibilities\" section is included from <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Chrome_incompatibilities\">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Chrome_incompatibilities</a> using the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Template:WebExtChromeCompat\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">WebExtChromeCompat</a> macro.</p>\n  <p>If you need to update this content, edit <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Chrome_incompatibilities\">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/Add-ons/WebExtensio